---

## Summary — everything in order
```
Step 1  Terminal          →  npx web-push generate-vapid-keys

Step 2  Render dashboard  →  Add env vars:
                              VAPID_PUBLIC_KEY, VAPID_PRIVATE_KEY,
                              VAPID_MAILTO, CRON_SECRET

Step 3  Supabase SQL      →  Paste + run the new CREATE TABLE block

Step 4  index.html        →  Add push <script> before </body>
                              Add 3 lines after initDemoNudges()

Step 5  sw.js             →  Full replace

Step 6  server.js         →  Add 2 lines to mount /push route

Step 7  package.json      →  Add 3 packages + update start script
                              Run: npm install

Step 8  routes/push.js         →  CREATE new file
        routes/nudge-engine.js →  CREATE new file
        cron.js                →  CREATE new file at root

Step 9  git push backend  →  Render auto-deploys
        git push frontend →  Netlify auto-deploys
